FCR22AU.original: ~z~Cousin, you will be shooting pool alone today. Do not place bets, okay?
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~堂兄，今天你只能自己打台球了。不要赌钱，好吧？

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_GETCALL_SPEC
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_GETCALL_SPEC

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Roman, is your cousin. Any chance of getting a cab?
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~Roman，是你堂弟。能不能派辆车过来？

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_HILIKE
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_HILIKE

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Sure Roman, I'll come and get you in the next hour.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~当然，Roman，我一小时内来接你。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Niko, I am too sick to walk. Please get me a car.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~Niko，我现在走不了路。拜托给我弄辆车。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Roman, sorry but I cannot bowl with you anymore. Another time.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~Roman，很抱歉，但我不能陪你打保龄球了。改天吧。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Cousin, our drunkenness will have to wait. Something has happened.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~堂兄，我们的酒虫该等等了。突然有事。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~That is cool, cousin. We do this on another occasion.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~没关系，堂弟。我们可以改天再约。

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_GAMES_CANCEL
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_GAMES_CANCEL

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Niko, get your invalid cousin a car. He cannot walk in this state.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~Niko，给你行动不便的堂兄找辆车。他现在没法走路。

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_CALL_REQ_SPEC_YES
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_CALL_REQ_SPEC_YES

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Thanks, Niko. See you then.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~谢了，Niko。待会儿见。

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_CALL_SPEC_END
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_CALL_SPEC_END

FCR22AU.original: ~z~I am sorry, cousin, but I must cancel our bowling.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~很抱歉，堂兄，但我们不能去打保龄球了。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Sorry, Roman. I cannot play pool with you anymore. I have another plan.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~抱歉，Roman。我没法来跟你打台球了。有别的事要做。

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_REQ_SPEC
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_REQ_SPEC

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Alright then, I might get cab or something.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~那好吧，我叫辆车算了。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Sorry cousin, but I don't have no cabs right now. You must call again later.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~抱歉，堂弟，但我现在也没车可派了。你得待会儿再打过来了。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Niko, as you are my cousin I want you to use family business how you like. Any time you want cab, you call me.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~Niko，既然你是我的堂弟，我想让你随意利用我们的家族产业。什么时候想打车了，给我打个电话。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Okay, Niko. We shall rain check this for a different occasion.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~好的，Niko。我们就推迟到别的时间吧。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Roman, you need to play a single player game. I can not hang out.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~Roman，你只能自己去玩了，我陪不了你了。

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_SHOW_CANCEL
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_SHOW_CANCEL

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_HOSP_CANCEL_B_UA
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_HOSP_CANCEL_B_UA

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Niko, I am sorry but nothing is available. You must call back another time.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~Niko，很抱歉，但是现在没车了。你还是过会儿再打过来吧。

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_PRO_GETCALL_HOSP_NO
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_PRO_GETCALL_HOSP_NO

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Thank you for picking me up, cousin. Will you take me home?
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~感谢你来接我，堂弟。能送我回家吗？

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_CALL_REQ_SPEC_NO
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_CALL_REQ_SPEC_NO

FCR22AU.original: ~z~You are a life saver, cousin. I'll see you soon.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~你真是我的救星，堂弟。我们一会儿见。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~You need walk no longer. There's a cab coming to you.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~你用不着再徒步了，有辆车往你这儿来了。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~You will leave your own cousin to walk home sick. Okay, Niko.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~你居然让刚出院的堂兄走回家。行吧，Niko。

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_STRIP_CANCEL
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_STRIP_CANCEL

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_ASK
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_ASK

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Sorry Roman, you may have to drink alone. I can no longer join you.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~抱歉，Roman，你可能要一个人喝酒了。我没法陪你了。

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_PRO_GETCALL_SPEC_END_C_CA
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_PRO_GETCALL_SPEC_END_C_CA

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Cousin, you must dine alone. I can no longer join you.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~堂兄，你只能自己吃饭了。我不能陪你了。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~You are a good cousin. Thank you for collecting me. I need to go home now.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~真是个好堂弟，感谢你来接我。我现在要回家了。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Alright, Niko. We shall do this another time. Later on.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~好吧，Niko。我们改天再约吧。回见。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Niko, you are just fooling with me. Thanks a lot.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~Niko，你是存心耍我吧。多谢了。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Niko, I'm being discharged from the hospital. Would you mind picking me up?
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~Niko，医院让我出院了。你介意来接我一趟吗？

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Sorry, cousin. I cannot join you at the tittie bar. You can still go by yourself though.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~抱歉，堂兄。我没法陪你去奶子吧了。不过你还是能自己去。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Thank you, cousin. That could be very useful in this city.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~谢了，堂兄。在这里会很有用的。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Alright, cousin. Maybe another time you will feel like being part of the family.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~好吧，堂弟。下次想和家人团聚了记得找我。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Wait right there, NB. I'm dispatching one now.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~原地等着，NB。我这就派车过来。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Sorry, Roman. I can't do it right now. Can't you get Mallorie to do it?
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~抱歉，Roman，我现在来不了。你就不能让Mallorie来接吗？

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Don't worry cousin, I have hot bitches that are begging me for my company, see you soon.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~别担心，堂弟，很多性感的贱人求我陪呢，之后见。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Cousin, I can't play no games with you just now. Sorry.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~Cousin, I can't play no games with you just now. Sorry.

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Cousin, I'm getting out of hospital. You couldn't pick me up could you?
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~堂弟，我出院了。能麻烦你来接我一趟吗？

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_EAT_CANCEL
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_EAT_CANCEL

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_MEDLIKE
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_MEDLIKE

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Sure, Niko. We can always do this another time. I see you then.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~好的，Niko。总会有机会的。之后见。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Roman. I can't eat with you. This may help you lose some weight.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~Roman，我没法和你一起吃饭了。说不定还能帮你减减肥。

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_REJ_HILIKE
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_REJ_HILIKE

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Hey, Roman. You mind if we catch the show on another night? I have something else to do.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~嘿，Roman。你介意改天再去看表演吗？我现在有别的事情要做。

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_CALL_HOSP_CANCEL_MEDLIKE
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_CALL_HOSP_CANCEL_MEDLIKE

FCR22AU.original: ~z~I will remember this next time you are in trouble, Niko. I will remember.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~这笔帐我会记着的，下次你有事了当心点，Niko。我都记着呢。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~You are my cousin, Niko. How can I refuse? There is a cab on its way.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~你可是我堂弟啊，Niko。我怎么能拒绝呢？已经有辆车在路上了。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Cousin, I hope you are not forgetting your family in this city? We do this on different occasion.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~堂弟，你应该没忘了自由城的家人吧？我们以后再约吧。

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_BOWL_CANCEL
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_BOWL_CANCEL

FCR22AU.original: ~z~I am sorry cousin, but I have no time. I'll see you soon though.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~抱歉，堂兄，但我没空。还是改天再见吧。

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_LOLIKE
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_LOLIKE

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Roman, it's Niko. I need a cab.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~Roman，我是Niko。我要打车。

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVEF_HOSPITAL
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVEF_HOSPITAL

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Roman, I cannot go look at titties with you. I have to do something else.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~Roman，我不能陪你去看奶子了。有别的事情要做。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Anything for you, NB. It should be there soon.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~有需要你就直说，NB。应该马上就到。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Really, Niko. I told everyone you were coming to get me. I will have to walk now.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~真的，Niko？我告诉了所有人你会来接我。现在只能走回家了。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Roman, my cousin, I'd really like a cab if you could send one to me.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~Roman，好堂兄，我很希望你能给我派辆出租车。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Sorry, cousin. I cannot see the show with you no more. Hope that's cool.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~抱歉，堂兄，我不能和你去看表演了。希望没事。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Hey Roman, you couldn't send a cab for a cousin in need could you?
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~嘿，Roman，能不能给你堂弟派辆车过来？

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_HOSPITAL_DROPOFF
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_HOSPITAL_DROPOFF

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_POOL_CANCEL
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_POOL_CANCEL

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_REJ_MEDLIKE
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_REJ_MEDLIKE

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Cousin, you do not have much family here, you should treat me with more respect. Maybe another time soon. Okay.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~堂弟，你在这里只有我一个家人，对我好一点好吗。那就下次再约吧。

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_DRINK_CANCEL
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_DRINK_CANCEL

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_CALL_HOSP_CANCEL_LOLIKE
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_CALL_HOSP_CANCEL_LOLIKE

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_DARTS_CANCEL
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_DARTS_CANCEL

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Hey Roman, sorry to fuck you round but I don't need no cab no more.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~嘿，Roman，很抱歉给你添麻烦了，但我不需要打车了。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~That's cool, cousin. Call again if you actually do need one.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~没关系，堂弟。下次需要了记得找我。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Sorry, Roman. Something has come up. I cannot throw darts with you now.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~抱歉，Roman。突然有点急事，没法跟你去玩飞镖了。

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_PRO_GETCALL_HOSP_YES
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_PRO_GETCALL_HOSP_YES

FCR22AU.original: ~z~I can do that for my cousin, I shouldn't take longer than an hour to get there.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~自家兄弟怎么不接，应该不用一个小时就能到。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Thanks for the ride, Niko. Call me soon, yes.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~谢谢你送我回家，Niko。记得联系，好吗。

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_CANCEL_SPEC_C_GA
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_PRO_CALL_CANCEL_SPEC_C_GA

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Cousin, I am no longer able to do darts with you. Sorry.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~堂兄，我没法来跟你玩飞镖了。抱歉。

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_HOSPITAL
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_HOSPITAL

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_REJ_LOLIKE
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_REJ_LOLIKE

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Okay cousin, if you have no time you have no time.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~好吧，堂弟，你没空就没空吧。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~Roman, I'm sorry but something has come up and I can no longer pick you up from the hospital.
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~Roman，很对不起，但我突然有急事，不能来医院接你了。

FCR22AU.original: ~z~You are kind for giving me a lift, Niko. Call your sick cousin soon, okay?
FCR22AU.translated: ~z~你能来接我真好，Niko。记得给你体弱的堂兄打电话，好吧？

FCR22AU.original: FCR2_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_ACCEPT
FCR22AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_ACCEPT
